261
00:31:43,229 --> 00:31:46,221
The violinist's really very talented.

262
00:32:03,669 --> 00:32:05,660
What is it?

263
00:32:05,829 --> 00:32:08,821
What is it?
- Paulette.

264
00:32:10,869 --> 00:32:13,861
