You had big burning hands and
you tore off my clothes.

274
00:32:55,229 --> 00:32:58,301
Paulette, please,
leave my shirt on.

275
00:32:59,229 --> 00:33:03,188
You've torn it. Are you happy now?
You're hurting me.

276
00:33:03,230 --> 00:33:07,667
Hold me with all your strength.
- Stop. You're making me fall.

277
00:33:10,229 --> 00:33:13,619
Oh, François...
- Paulette! Paulette! Paulette! Paulette!

278
00:33:14,429 --> 00:33:17,501
Paulette!
- François! François! François!

279
00:33:17,629 --> 00:33:21,019
François! François! François!
- Paulette! Paulette! Paulette!

280
00:33:21,549 --> 00:33:24,541
François!
- Paulette! Ah, Paulette!

281
00:33:24,829 --> 00:33:27,821
François...
- Paulette! Paulette!

282
00:33:28,230 --> 00:33:31,108
François...
- Paulette.

283
00:33:31,229 --> 00:33:34,107
How does a horse sound?
- No.

284
