Yes, how does a horse sound?
- No.

285
00:33:45,709 --> 00:33:48,701
Shit, shit, shit, shit, shit.

286
00:33:49,949 --> 00:33:52,543
Stop that, shit!

287
00:34:21,229 --> 00:34:25,142
So, was Munich nice?
- I'm really a loser.

288
