Yes, a bicycle.

324
00:37:14,710 --> 00:37:16,063
I want a photo.

325
00:37:19,309 --> 00:37:23,427
He's supposed to go to the park,
unless he decides to go to the dentist now.

326
00:37:26,644 --> 00:37:28,520
Don't be stupid, Maurice!

327
00:37:35,333 --> 00:37:37,409
Don't be stupid, Maurice!

328
00:37:43,229 --> 00:37:46,301
