334
00:38:24,509 --> 00:38:26,500
Shit!

335
00:38:33,109 --> 00:38:36,101
Look at those little bikes.
Having a flat?

336
00:38:37,109 --> 00:38:40,499
No, we're playing a game.
- There's no more quality, these days.

337
00:38:41,229 --> 00:38:45,188
I remember before the war...
I'm talking before the war, gentlemen...

338
00:38:45,229 --> 00:38:49,188
