348
00:39:46,789 --> 00:39:50,702
Paulette! Hello, Paulette.
I have to talk to you, Paulette.

349
00:39:50,790 --> 00:39:55,227
I've been thinking a lot in Munich.
We can't go on like this.

350
00:40:01,229 --> 00:40:04,619
A good shower
and you'll feel great.

351
00:40:05,229 --> 00:40:08,301
What's that?
- Listen, Maurice...

352
00:40:08,429 --> 00:40:12,217
