00:44:03,829 --> 00:44:06,821
Hello, yes? Musical instruments?

400
00:44:08,429 --> 00:44:12,388
Musical instruments. Old ones.
Go to some antique shops and...

401
00:44:12,429 --> 00:44:16,388
