I'm glad the others are gone.

447
00:52:16,389 --> 00:52:19,779
So nice. A bit of intimacy
from time to time.

448
00:52:20,429 --> 00:52:23,421
Yes, that's true... that's true...

449
00:52:25,629 --> 00:52:29,542
