01:22:58,229 --> 01:23:02,188
Everything will be back to
the way it was, darling.

709
01:23:03,869 --> 01:23:07,145
Better go home.
He'll catch a cold.

710
01:23:07,829 --> 01:23:09,626
Come.

711
01:23:12,829 --> 01:23:15,901
Have a good trip. Be good in Munich.
- Bye bye.

712
01:23:23,229 --> 01:23:26,619
Going to Munich?
- No. To Rio, in Brazil.

713
01:23:27,229 --> 01:23:30,301
Ah, to Rio.
That's not the same desk.

714
01:23:30,710 --> 01:23:33,782
No, let me.
I'll check it in myself.

715
01:23:34,629 --> 01:23:37,223
Hey, sir!

716
01:23:50,949 --> 01:23:54,339
Christine? Are you alright?
- I'd be better in your arms.

717
01:23:55,229 --> 01:23:58,107
Do you love me?
- Yes, I love you.

718
01:24:02,629 --> 01:24:05,701
When he'll be back from Rio...
- Yes, sir.

719
01:24:06,630 --> 01:24:10,020
...and come back he will,
you must contact him.

720
01:24:12,629 --> 01:24:16,622
After all,
the guy has a talent.

721
01:24:23,697 --> 01:24:31,478
Everybody has the right
to a private life.

722
01:24:31,754 --> 01:24:35,495
Article 9 of the Penal Code.

723
01:24:35,866 --> 01:24:41,768
THE TALL BLOND GUY WITH A BLACK SHOE

